TEXT.S: Kakako pasiiked sofol : ma'oripay, salawacan :a'adopen, fawahan :sakololay, opir :pacocoay, mata :tosa sackih, : fafoy, :fafoy, fafoy o otimo o micopcopay to hacal, maedeng 220 ko kasasiroma' nira, ona otimo tahanini i, tangasa 90 saheto o iraay ko cakecih, itini tona ci cakecihay a a'a'dopen o kolong ko saadihayay.
